strings.Value: "Bless us, oh goddess. Give us wings, and your blight shall soar. Give us power, and all shall fulfill your will..."
"I eat and drink to the glory of Lady Despair. I take from life, to give to death. I take from the poor, to feed the sated..."
"Ugh... By the gods... Ahem, friends, I'm not hungry at all today! Who wants my share?"
"Oh. And I thought that after that giant centipede dissection nothing would ever ruin my appetite again..."
"Oh, it's bad luck to keep company with the dead. And having one of those in a party..."
"Chomp chomp chomp... What? She-dead wasn't eating hers anyway!"
